metadata.name: Quincy Douby | New Jersey Legends Series 1 | Digital
metadata.description: Quincy Douby (Rutgers 2003-2006) was named to the Big East All-Rookie Team his freshman year and All Big-East team as a junior in 2005-06 when he was the conference scoring leader. In 2006, he was drafted as the 19th pick by the Sacramento Kings and later played for several teams in Europe.
